---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About VaultMill">
  <section class="page">
    <h1>About VaultMill</h1>

    <p>
      VaultMill is building a trusted knowledge platform for executive
      leadership.
    </p>

    <p>
      Information about executives is often spread across company
      websites, press releases, regulatory filings, news articles, and
      social networks. VaultMill brings that information together into a
      structured, searchable resource that makes it easier to understand
      the people leading today's organizations.
    </p>

    <p>
      Our platform goes beyond executive biographies. We connect leaders
      with the companies, boards, investors, and organizations they have
      served, creating a richer picture of careers, leadership teams, and
      professional networks. By organizing these relationships,
      VaultMill helps users discover meaningful context—not just isolated
      facts.
    </p>

    <p>
      Built with modern AI and structured data, VaultMill continuously
      organizes and enhances publicly available information while
      emphasizing accuracy, transparency, and usability. Every profile is
      designed to evolve as careers and organizations change over time.
    </p>

    <p>
      VaultMill serves investors, recruiters, executive search firms,
      journalists, researchers, consultants, business development teams,
      and anyone who needs reliable executive intelligence.
    </p>

    <p>
      Our mission is simple: transform fragmented public information into
      organized knowledge that helps people understand leadership and
      make better business decisions.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>